data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Jones’s personal touches and upgraded features will be sure to make you feel at home. Throughout the home, rustic modern beams line the ceilings in addition to elevated fixtures. This open floor plan and rear sliding patio doors allows for ample natural light throughout the living space.     The kitchen features custom cabinetry with crown molding, matte black hardware, recessed lighting, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, pantry and breakfast bar that is open to the dining nook. In addition, the first floor features an additional room that can be used as a main floor bedroom, mother in law suite, or at home office.     Follow the stairs to the second floor where you will find comfort in the Primary Suite and Ensuite. Upgrades here feature barn doors, a free standing tub, dual vanity, and walk in closet.     Relax on the fully enclosed private brick patio, perfect for hosting family and friends all year round, or take a swim in the community’s pool. When you are not enjoying all Jones’s as to offer, just as short drive away you will find yourself in the middle of Lake Nona’s Town Center, Tavistock’s popular restaurants, Boxi Park, The Wave Hotel and its popular restaurants, Bacon, Haven, Nami, shopping amenities, and more. Once you live here, you won’t want to live anywhere else.
